~ exitOffice_1
do Global.grabCameraPos()
do Global.moveCamera(Vector2(0,25))
do Global.zoomCamera(Vector2(2.5,2.5))
Kite: The sun is shining [wave amp=20 freq=5]brightly[/wave] upon us Lady Makoto! Allow us to venture forth with justice in our hearts in pursuit of truth. [#expression_left=unimp][#expression_right=happy][#animate_right=enter_convo][#actor_right=on][#new_actor=kite_right]
Makoto shakes her head and steps out into the East River District.
do Global.finishOneShot("openingDone")
do Global.zoomCamera(Vector2(1.5,1.5))
do Global.resetCamera()
