do Global.markPreviousQuest(load("res://Assets/Quests/Quest10.tres"))
do Signals.updateInfoAnimation.emit("notebook")
do Global.zoomCamera(Vector2(2.5,2.5))
do Global.resetCamera()
=> END

~ firstEnterYokaiRealm
do Global.grabCameraPos()
do Global.moveCamera(Vector2(0,25))
do Global.zoomCamera(Vector2(2.5,2.5))
Makoto: Whoa… [#expression_left=confused][#expression_right=neutral][#actor_right=on][#new_actor=kite_right]
Kite: Well well! Is this not a joyous sight for these tenured eyes! [#animate_right=enter_convo][#expression_right=happy][#animate_left=exit_convo]
Makoto: Kite, what are you talking about? Where are we? [#animate_right=exit_convo][#animate_left=enter_convo][#expression_left=unimp]
Kite: Well my lady! Do you feel how the energy flows through the air here? We’ve ended up in the [outline_size=5][color=aquamarine][wave amp=20 freq=5]spirit realm![/wave][/color][/outline_size] The land that was once my home. [#animate_left=exit_convo][#animate_right=enter_convo]
Makoto: The spirit realm? Why is there an entrance to the spirit realm here? [#animate_right=exit_convo][#animate_left=enter_convo][#expression_left=confused]
Kite: The mortal realm and spirit realm are ever interconnected. You’re as likely to find a place to cross over in an old alley as a shrine in the woods. [#animate_left=exit_convo][#animate_right=enter_convo]
Makoto: There’s a lot I want to ask, but we need to find that florist. [#animate_right=exit_convo][#animate_left=enter_convo][#expression_left=angry]
Kite: Well then, onwards, my lady! FOR JUSTICE! [#animate_left=exit_convo][#animate_right=enter_convo]
Take a moment to review all of your information and evidence, then proceed onwards. [#actor_left=off][#actor_right=off]
do Global.finishOneShot("PortalFound")
do Global.questsList.quests.append(load("res://Assets/Quests/Quest12.tres"))
do Global.markPreviousQuest(load("res://Assets/Quests/Quest11.tres"))
do Signals.updateInfoAnimation.emit("notebook")
do Global.zoomCamera(Vector2(1.5,1.5))
do Global.resetCamera()
=> END
